org.jcvi.jillion.sam.header

Interface SamProgram


  • public interface SamProgram
    SamProgram contains information about a specific program and its invocation used in the pipeline that generated this SAM File.
    Author:
    dkatzel

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      String getCommandLine()
      Get the Commandline invocation of the program.
      String getDescription()
      Description of the program.
      String getId()
      Get the unique ID.
      String getName()
      Get the program name.
      String getPreviousProgramId()
      Get the Id of the previous SamProgram that operated on this SAM file.
      String getVersion()
      Version of the program.

    • Method Detail

      • getId

        String getId()
        Get the unique ID. The value of ID is used in the ReservedSamAttributeKeys.PROGRAM tag.
        Returns:
        a String; will never be null.

      • getName

        String getName()
        Get the program name.
        Returns:
        the name of this program as a String; may be null if this information is not provided.

      • getVersion

        String getVersion()
        Version of the program.
        Returns:
        the version as a String; may be null if not provided.

      • getDescription

        String getDescription()
        Description of the program.
        Returns:
        the description of what this program does as a String; may be null if not provided.

      • getCommandLine

        String getCommandLine()
        Get the Commandline invocation of the program.
        Returns:
        the commandline used to invoke this program does as a String; may be null if not provided.

      • getPreviousProgramId

        String getPreviousProgramId()
        Get the Id of the previous SamProgram that operated on this SAM file.
        Returns:
        an Id String or null if this is the last (or only) program in the chain.
